```mermaid
graph TD
    Start[User Query: Vague] --> Clarif1[Clarification Node]
    
    Clarif1 --> Check1{Query Clear?}
    
    Check1 -->|Yes| Plan1[Planning Node<br/>Uses: original_query]
    Check1 -->|No| Store1[Store clarification_message]
    
    Store1 --> Return1[Return to User<br/>Ask for clarification]
    
    Return1 --> UserResp[User Provides<br/>Clarification Response]
    
    UserResp --> Clarif2[Clarification Node<br/>Re-entry]
    
    Clarif2 --> Preserve[PRESERVE Context:<br/>✅ original_query unchanged<br/>✅ clarification_message preserved<br/>✅ user_clarification_response stored]
    
    Preserve --> Combine[CREATE combined_query_context:<br/>Original Query + Clarification + Response]
    
    Combine --> Plan2[Planning Node<br/>Uses: combined_query_context]
    
    Plan1 --> SQL[SQL Synthesis]
    Plan2 --> SQL
    
    SQL --> Exec[SQL Execution]
    
    Exec --> Summary[Result Summary]
    
    Summary --> End1[End - Results Returned]
    
    End1 -.Follow-up Query.-> FollowUp[ask_follow_up_query]
    
    FollowUp --> ThreadMem[Thread Memory<br/>Restores previous context]
    
    ThreadMem --> NewClarif[Clarification Node<br/>With previous context]
    
    NewClarif --> Plan3[Planning Node<br/>Has access to previous conversation]
    
    Plan3 --> SQL2[SQL Synthesis<br/>With conversation context]
    
    SQL2 --> Exec2[SQL Execution]
    
    Exec2 --> Summary2[Result Summary]
    
    Summary2 --> End2[End - Follow-up Results]
    
